xyz.fsgik.common.bean

接口 FsBeanResolver


  • @ThreadSafe
public interface FsBeanResolver
    Resolver for FsBean, usually consists of FsBeanResolver.Handlers. There are 2 built-in resolvers:
    • JavaBeanResolveHandler (default handler);
    • RecordBeanResolveHandler;
    And a skeletal implementation: AbstractBeanResolveHandler.

      • defaultResolver

        static FsBeanResolver defaultResolver()
        Returns default bean resolver of which handler is JavaBeanResolveHandler.

      • newResolver

        static FsBeanResolver newResolver(FsBeanResolver.Handler handler)
        Returns new bean resolver with given handler and FsCache.softCache(). This method is equivalent to newResolver(Iterable): 
             return newResolver(Collections.singleton(handler));
        参数:
        handler - given handler
        返回:
        new bean resolver

      • newResolver

        static FsBeanResolver newResolver(java.lang.Iterable<FsBeanResolver.Handler> handlers)
        Returns new bean resolver with given handlers and FsCache.softCache(). This method is equivalent to newResolver(Iterable, FsCache): 
             return newResolver(handlers, FsCache.softCache());
        参数:
        handlers - given handlers
        返回:
        new bean resolver

      • newResolver

        static FsBeanResolver newResolver(java.lang.Iterable<FsBeanResolver.Handler> handlers,
                                  @Nullable
                                  @Nullable FsCache<java.lang.reflect.Type,FsBean> cache)
        Returns new bean resolver with given handlers and cache option. If given cache is null, returned resolver will not cache the resolved bean.
        参数:
        handlers - given handlers
        cache - given cache
        返回:
        new bean resolver

      • resolve

        FsBean resolve(java.lang.reflect.Type type)

        参数:

        返回:

      • wrapMap

        default FsBean wrapMap(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> map)
        Wraps given map as a FsBean, of which type will be seen as Map<String, Object>. This method is same with: 
             wrapMap(map, null);
        参数:
        map - given map
        返回:
        wrapped FsBean
        另请参阅:
        wrapMap(Map, Type)

      • wrapMap

        default FsBean wrapMap(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,?> map,
                       @Nullable
                       @Nullable java.lang.reflect.Type mapType)
        Wraps given map as a FsBean, the key type of map type must be String. If the given map type is null, the map type will be seen as DEFAULT_MAP_BEAN_TYPE.

        Result of FsBean.getProperties() is immutable, but content may be different for each time calling. Because of the changes in given map, contents of return property map are also changed accordingly.

        参数:
        map - given map
        mapType - given map type
        返回:
        wrapped FsBean

      • insertFirstHandler

        default FsBeanResolver insertFirstHandler(FsBeanResolver.Handler handler)
        Returns a new resolver of which handlers come from current resolver, but inserts given handler at first index of handlers. The returned resolver will share the cache with this resolver.
        参数:
        handler - given handler
        返回:
        a new resolver

        返回:
        a new resolver
